cs.SE, cs.CY, cs.SI, cs.PL, cs.LG. 

This paper focuses on the analysis of bot commits in social coding platforms, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) sub-category. The use of association rule mining to identify the types of files modified together suggests a focus on data mining and analysis (cs.CY) and machine learning (cs.LG). The examination of the frequency and type of files added/ deleted/ modified by the commits suggests a focus on software infrastructure (cs.SI) and programming languages (cs.PL).
